data.description: Move-in ready 4/2 in Cimarron with an oversized covered back patio! The fourth bedroom has double doors to the patio and would make a nice office or study. The newer roof had the complete decking replaced. HVAC is approx 5 years old and the water heater is approx 3 years old.  Other updates include granite countertops and tile and wood laminate flooring. The laundry room is between the kitchen and garage and has a separate drop area. The kitchen island is free-standing and can be moved according to your needs. One side of the home has concrete for convenience and leads to a doggie door into the utility room. The primary suite has his and her closets and a tiled walk-in shower. Wood burning fireplace in the living room has a convenient clean-out outside. The garage had been a mancave and has faux brick walls and a painted floor. Storage building in the backyard. Range and refrigerator will convey.
